Roxana McGowan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roxana_McGowan 0 Roxana McGowan (March 15, 1897 – November 22, 1976), born in Chicago, Illinois, was an actress in Mack Sennett comedies in the silent film era. Her screen career was brief, lasting from 1917–1919.
